<title>UK: ABB unit adds 100 million Swiss francs to bond.</title>
<headline>ABB unit adds 100 million Swiss francs to bond.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following bond has been increased to 250 million Swiss francs from 150 million Swiss francs, lead manager UBS said.</p>
<p> BORROWER   ABB INTERNATIONAL FINANCE NV CURACAO</p>
<p>KEEPWELL AGREEMENT WITH ABB ASEA BROWN BOVERI</p>
<p> AMT   *100 MLN CHF   COUPON     3.0	 MATURITY    25.SEP.02</p>
<p> TYPE	 STRAIGHT  ISS PRICE  102.05    PAY DATE  S-05.JUN.97</p>
<p> FULL FEES  STANDARD  LISTING    EBS	 EOS	   22.MAY.97</p>
<p> DENOMS (K) FIVE	GOV LAW    SWISS     SALE LIMITS US/NV</p>
<p> NEG PLG    YES	 CRS DEFLT   YES	FORCE MAJ   YES</p>
<p> NOTES    S-SHORT FIRST COUPON</p>
<p>	    *FUNGIBLE ON PAY DATE, ORIGINAL LAUNCHED 10.FEB.97</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
